moe moe moe moe moe moe moe moe moe moe  <<3

OMFG OMFG OMFG OMFG!!!!!!!!!!!

Okay....now...Last night (and this morning),
I got the best dream I eva had!!!
Last night I was playing KH2 for the fifth time before go to sleep, also reading some fanfiction on Final Fantasy VII. 

The first dream is about FFVII. I was talking to Tifa at the 7th Heaven, 
before Yuffie bursting in...and...I scream AHHHHHHHHHH!!!! and 
Yuffie also scream out AHHHHHH!!!! After that Cloud comes
 in, then I and Yuffie scream again, due to we surprised that Cloudy came in. 
Not only that...Cloud also scream = = After that Cid, Red, Cat, Barret bursted in 
(in order that I listed too) screaming the shit out of them self = [] =!!!
Then, the emo king, Vicent V. came in, sweatdrop on his head, 
giving the screaming idiots a funny look, before he says to
 Tifa "Punch meh on the face right here...here..."
Then I woke up giggling LOOOOL
Like, Oh mah gooshhh

Then I went to sleep...Now this time I notice myself at Disney world .
..waiting to go on something, can't remeber...Then I heard someone
 shout "OI!!! You there! Come here!!!" Then things that surprised me is that, it actually got a Japanese subtitle 
when someone say something!!!! But the speaking is 
in English...and english is not me first lang.!!!!
I turn to look and saw...Xemnas!!! Then he start to run ta meh...
and yup...I start to run away from him. I took a sharp turn and went in to a 
'Staff Only' room thingy. I ended up in a blue wall maze! 
Running away from him, taking a sharp left and right turn. 
I seems to be running in circle though. AND after the 651984368th turns, 
I saw Micky running passed me with Xigbar on his tail!!! I shouted to him 
"Why dun you just fight him???" he reply "And why dun you Fight HIM!!!" while pointing to Xemnas
"I dun have a weapon!!!"
"Then use your Keyblade!"

WTF =_="

And I saw other bunch of main character running away from other Organ.XIII memmber...

Sora - Roxas
Riku - Axel
Kairi - Demyx
and so on~

And to one point, I saw a door lead to outside.
I open it and went outside.
Hiding behide the box...
Xemnas comes out and start ranting like "I know you're here blah 
blah blah...Kingdom Hearts...blah blah" and he went inside the building again...
After that Saix come out with marluxia.
The pink head start to rant, then Saix found me...
"WTF what do u want with me????"
"I...dunno, why do you run away then?"
"I was scare shitless damnit"
"= = Oh..."

Then I woke up...End!!!!

LOOOOOLL

First entry and I already ranting damnit

OK...now lets start off why I say mah christmas gonna suck. 
It all start of when my parent and I argue about where to go on halidays this year.
I and my sister say we want to go to Tokyo Disney World, and also some game shopping
at Akihabara (where they sale games and otaku stuff...I really want that Roxas and Axel model).
BUT noooooo~ My parent want to go Europe Tour, and spend Christmas at Paris
When that didn't work out, we talked bout going to Africa, oh my god, isn't that nice.
In the end, we wnd up going up north to stay up in the mountain...

Not only that, my father also got into a fight with his brother, about the fortune will thingie, and turn out that, I'm NOT gonna get ANYTHING for christmas this year!!!!
